Permissions

By using this software, users agree to cite the source of the software in any publications or software distributions that incorporate or use any part of this software. The citation should adhere to the following format:

Gemalmaz, M., & Yin, M. (2021, August). Accounting for Confirmation Bias in Crowdsourced Label Aggregation. In Proceedings of the Thirtieth International Joint Conference on Artificial Intelligence.

This citation format is required in academic publications or any other medium where the software forms a part of the research or development that is being published.

